            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Steve Blank's formula is: "We help [X] do [Y] by [Z]." For example: "We help content marketers publish 10x more SEO content by automating research, briefs, and scheduling." It forces clarity on the customer segment, the outcome they want, and the mechanism by which you deliver it.</p></div></div>
          </div>
